                &kp GLOBE, &none,     &none,     &none,     &none,     &none,    &kp HOME,    &kp PG_UP, &none,     &none,         &none,         &none,         &none,           &none,
                                      &none,     &none,     &none,     &none,    &kp END,     &kp PG_DN, &mkp MB2,  &mkp MB1,       &mkp MB3,      &none,         &molock
            )>;
